  "short_description": "Playtown is a horror game set in a kid's dinosaur-themed indoor playground. Roam the kids play areas, pipe lands and ball pits to uncover and find your daughter's necklace, while unraveling the mystery surrounding the once happy place. Remember .. you are not alone.",
