  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/75e56ad6a36679900d7faae2525747eb.avif?t=1716900663\" width=601 height=170 /></span><br><br><strong>Playtown</strong> is a first person adventure horror game that takes place inside a kid's indoor playground. Play as a loving father that is tasked to find his daughter's missing necklace but beware - as danger can be lurking in every corner. Evade traps, solve mind-bending puzzles to your destination while trying to stay alive and explore the mysterious playground... but don't get caught.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Captivating story and puzzles to solve</h2>Explore what was once a place filled with joy and experience the wonders of a emotional journey into finding your daughter's lost necklace inside a big indoor playground. A captivating adventure horror game that will tug at your heartstrings. Step into the shoes of a loving father determined to find and reunite his daughter with her precious necklace.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mind-Bending Puzzles</h2>Solve puzzles and try to stay alive in what once was once seen as an amusing attraction. The player is tasked with solving puzzles in order to get to their right destination with dangers lurking at every corner. Every step you will take can be a deadly, so make your choice wisely.. and don't loose your sanity.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The dinosaur-themed indoor park was once the dream place of every child!</h2>The dinosaur-theme indoor playground was once the go-to place for every child to be filled with joy. Steg the dinosaur was everybody's favourite, however nobody knows what happens in the playground behind closed doors. Now you must explore the establishment and uncover some nasty secrets.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore pipe dreams, ball pits, and fun places to be around!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/3ce0f7b973e6c43946264f127e58b989.poster.avif?t=1716900663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/3ce0f7b973e6c43946264f127e58b989.webm?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/3ce0f7b973e6c43946264f127e58b989.mp4?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be always cautious of any dangers that may lurk inside.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/33667f90e320ff9c5a4fa1989dcbd78c.poster.avif?t=1716900663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/33667f90e320ff9c5a4fa1989dcbd78c.webm?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/33667f90e320ff9c5a4fa1989dcbd78c.mp4?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenging puzzles that will try to stop you from your goal.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/c9f598584af2b3d6d2e7bd6c31457908.poster.avif?t=1716900663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/c9f598584af2b3d6d2e7bd6c31457908.webm?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/c9f598584af2b3d6d2e7bd6c31457908.mp4?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Terrifying ambiance that can turn deadly at any step you'll take.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/59db4e73e02e7bf26dd2de647b27e8a9.poster.avif?t=1716900663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/59db4e73e02e7bf26dd2de647b27e8a9.webm?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/59db4e73e02e7bf26dd2de647b27e8a9.mp4?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Remember, the floor is lava from your childhood? This one is deadlier.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/c0a16befcabc58555abc533024071147.poster.avif?t=1716900663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/c0a16befcabc58555abc533024071147.webm?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/c0a16befcabc58555abc533024071147.mp4?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the kid's indoor playground place called - Playtown!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/9824ee3e02ba5b953a3ca593ed0b957a.poster.avif?t=1716900663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/9824ee3e02ba5b953a3ca593ed0b957a.webm?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/9824ee3e02ba5b953a3ca593ed0b957a.mp4?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find and uncover mysteries and puzzles to find out what happened in Playtown!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/90d0586e3ecd6198624d4fe7bfada631.poster.avif?t=1716900663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/90d0586e3ecd6198624d4fe7bfada631.webm?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/90d0586e3ecd6198624d4fe7bfada631.mp4?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- but be careful, you are not alone ... Steg the dino might get you! </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/cbab1a5da97770cc701188b1dbbafa8f.poster.avif?t=1716900663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/cbab1a5da97770cc701188b1dbbafa8f.webm?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588110/extras/cbab1a5da97770cc701188b1dbbafa8f.mp4?t=1716900663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Experience the story and uncover the mysteries of what happened inside Playtown.<br><br>Playtown is a horror game made by one developer. This is an indie adventure horror game with puzzles to solve, and terrifying encounters, pickup system, running, saving system and more. If you can, please submit your feedback and report any bugs and this will really help speed up the progress of the development. Thanks!",
